
 1. add fllowing code to pom.xml
 <reporting>
        <plugins>
            <plugin>
                <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
                <artifactId>maven-surefire-report-plugin</artifactId>
                <version>3.0.0-M4</version>
            </plugin>
        </plugins>
    </reporting>

    2. put the command to terminal
    mvn surefire-report:report